headline: One Tech Tip: Replacing passwords with passkeys for an easier login experience
summary: If you're tired of memorizing passwords, then give passkeys a try.  You might have noticed that many online services are now offering the option of using passkeys, a digital authentication method touted as an easier and more secure way to log in.  The passkey push started gaining major momentum after Google started accepting them about 18 months ago.
